{"tid":1687036,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【長文多圖】大家小心分化撚","createTime":"2019-11-01T14:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T17:25:21.000Z","uid":304945,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f82f52ddfd1c501354886ead391e56907477010","tid":1687036,"uid":304945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"分化撚真係日日有 呢兩日捉到一堆 <br />\n<br />\n事源係呢個message：<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f852fb07921c4158cd689.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Ff852fb07921c4158cd689.png&h=c0b6692d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1，來源：<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1295361187/3903934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1295361187%2F3903934&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8H9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=24a63845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1295361187/3903934</a><br />\n<br />\n咁我唔知大家同唔同意🥭a0毒撚芒果對佢嘅說話嘅詮釋啦：<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ef7e3e157f30f2f1e5b72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fef7e3e157f30f2f1e5b72.png&h=185c01fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2，來源：<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1295361187/3905100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1295361187%2F3905100&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8H9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=6bee2f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1295361187/3905100</a><br />\n由另一人cap圖，圖中原message已delete<br />\n<br />\n我就唔同意，🍎 同 🥥 亦唔同意。喺多方都唔肯讓步嘅情況之下，鬧交係無可避免。<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d9bd207a01c760009f2ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fd9bd207a01c760009f2ae.png&h=2ec222da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖3，🥭a0毒撚芒果嘅部分回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bd18a5192ab10ecfe5f17.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fbd18a5192ab10ecfe5f17.png&h=0ddeff89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖4，本人嘅部分回應<br />\n如果你對整個對話有興趣，建議由 <a href=\"https://t.me/c/1295361187/3903934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1295361187%2F3903934&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8H9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=24a63845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1295361187/3903934</a> 開始睇。<br />\n<br />\n後來呢個誰是誰非嘅討論就去咗谷務處理。由於已經入唔翻去cap圖，唯有用住我嘅backup先。<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0086dda4105730838bba0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2F0086dda4105730838bba0.png&h=323f8fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖5，我喺某D谷谷務嘅backup，欄位間以 &ldquo;|&rdquo; 分隔，按次序係message id，日期，作者，內容<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/efa3be5e54576adeb0b55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fefa3be5e54576adeb0b55.png&h=6a1fc033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖6，我喺某D谷谷務嘅backup，欄位間以 &ldquo;|&rdquo; 分隔，按次序係message id，日期，作者，內容<br />\n<br />\n當我幾日前因為另一件事同埋一句說話而俾 HKer ban，咁因為一句侮辱緊眾和理非嘅說話再加上拒絕道歉應該值得永久ban啦 (#6737)？<br />\n然而，眾admin不但拒絕ban 🥭a0毒撚芒果，同時話佢只係無心之失 (#6747)，對於同佢哋意見相左嘅就係 &ldquo;個人意見&rdquo; (#6762)，更加一直避談要求道歉嘅議題（可能係我文盲睇唔到？）<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/26f5d7734448bbd5eab88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2F26f5d7734448bbd5eab88.png&h=864841da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖7，HKer 依然堅持佢所謂嘅詮釋。來源：我同 HKer 分身嘅pm<br />\n<br />\nHKer 作為谷主更加認為道歉係冇必要，冒犯亦唔存在。重申一次我認為嘅和理非包括嘅範圍比 &ldquo;乜都唔做嗰啲人&rdquo; 呢個範圍闊好多。有人亦已經提出，上述嘅人應該叫 &ldquo;偽黃&rdquo; (#6837)。<br />\n件事嚟到呢度，誰是誰非已經好明顯。做錯就道歉，真係原來真係咁難。<br />\n然而事情一直冇進展。跟住就輪到 🥭a0毒撚芒果、🍎、🥥 同時被無限期停職。真停職定假停職下面會講。<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/547a0231da936603cb530.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2F547a0231da936603cb530.png&h=d407e54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖8，冇得罪人嘅都被停職。來源：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKDukerChannel/1555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKDukerChannel%2F1555&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8H9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=05e621ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKDukerChannel/1555</a> 狗=🥭a0毒撚芒果 mk=🥥 茄=🍎<br />\n<br />\n有鑒於出言不遜嘅 🥭a0毒撚芒果 只係退谷而冇被ban，再加上從上面谷務嘅對話而見，佢地並無意認錯道歉<br />\n而出言不遜嘅 🥭a0毒撚芒果 最後亦擁有admin嘅權限，反映圖9嘅情況係根本係惡人，實際情況只係假停職。成班根本都係分化撚互相包庇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/773e4822d37f0ba84d676.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2F773e4822d37f0ba84d676.png&h=0aff32c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖9，所謂停職，來源：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkdukerlogchannel/11433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkdukerlogchannel%2F11433&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8H9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=5a6d6187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkdukerlogchannel/11433</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e95045a9ceee9a7cab6a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fe95045a9ceee9a7cab6a2.png&h=c857f214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖10，🥭a0毒撚芒果復職當刻。來源：<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1295361187/3907939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1295361187%2F3907939&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8H9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=26a83ab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1295361187/3907939</a><br />\n<br />\n出言不遜嘅人係唔會被遺忘嘅，欠下嘅一句道歉係要還嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/85b8886e858475de1a5f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2F85b8886e858475de1a5f8.png&h=541f60c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖11，🍎 要求 🥭a0毒撚芒果 就佢之前嘅言論道歉<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5ee23d5caa90077c4c477.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2F5ee23d5caa90077c4c477.png&h=bcae383c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖12，🍎 要求 🥭a0毒撚芒果 就佢之前嘅言論道歉<br />\n<br />\n古天樂老婆🌻 認為 🍎 要 🥭 就話和理非係freeride嘅説話道歉，係回帶，係拉仇。唔通佢哋兩個有親？<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bd82765cbaa1683f78b25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fbd82765cbaa1683f78b25.png&h=ee581bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖13，🍎同古天樂老婆admin嘈左兩句後就去左貼文宣。有腦嘅都唔會同呢個分化撚嘈啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/db344e431896937383da9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fdb344e431896937383da9.png&h=5dc9e82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖14，當🍎問及古天樂老婆想🍎應佢咩<br />\n<br />\n而身為 admin 嘅 古天樂老婆🌻 不但拒絕公平咁處理件事，反而要滅聲。咁睇翻下面堆對話又好似唔似鬧交喎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8d6a0aff68277f9ee63b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2F8d6a0aff68277f9ee63b4.jpg&h=c9db6a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖15.1，我覺得幾和諧唔似鬧交<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ad7ea77b0fbd4f949869d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fad7ea77b0fbd4f949869d.jpg&h=eea557ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖15.2，我覺得幾和諧唔似鬧交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6c7cc0c5b61772877ec6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2F6c7cc0c5b61772877ec6b.png&h=29e0eba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖16.1<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d242ff19587228cfae6be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fd242ff19587228cfae6be.png&h=530918e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖16.2<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bcdd10a98ca7fefcefa22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fbcdd10a98ca7fefcefa22.png&h=f71d5529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖16.3<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ad3faa7795b04d7dd7447.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2Ffile%2Fad3faa7795b04d7dd7447.png&h=1e029255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖17，🍎向D谷主 Hker (又名JS) 反映<br />\n<br />\n谷主甚至對 🍎 嘅訴求視而不見，就好似林奠對popo惡行不見一樣。<br />\n<br />\n去到呢度根本就係為ban而ban，完全係打壓異己嘅行為。🍎 嘅訴求好簡單，就係得到一個就圖1中嗰句說話嘅一句道歉。<br />\n<br />\n至此，我認為對於啲分化撚係必須要制裁。<br />\n<br />\n而家 🥭 就話和理非係freeride去同和理非割蓆，而作為該谷admin，唔係要死攬硬攬，而係要同呢D分化撚割蓆。情況就好似黑警做錯野，同林奠話全力支持黑警一樣。而且個谷班 admin 已經同之前何妖開個人show一鳩樣。已經係一言堂。就同以家嘅中共一樣，有異見就ban。<br />\n<br />\n呢個谷表面上就黃，其實就係藍。已經同我地一班和理非割撚曬席，同今日嘅狗，林奠係無分別。<br />\n我懇請大家見到呢啲扮黃嘅獨裁谷同埋呢啲分化撚，要見一個，杯一個。<br />\nBy一個睇唔順眼嘅和理非<br />\n<br />\n最後不分化，不割蓆，<span style=\"color: red;\">仆街分化撚除外</span><br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n11.24 票投民建聯，全家玩撚完"},{"pid":"ca37d19219c48069c05cc7eee675edbf7e1bc7a2","tid":1687036,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"78d0144f90700059d3bf7579b4d4bad54eb25493","tid":1687036,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:19:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先40%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第二期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n民調眾籌LINK﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8H9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=e5e60e20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"7c509ab1e30ae7171fa98ba68a08f8117e7d76c9","tid":1687036,"uid":155339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母分化撚"},{"pid":"f56293e0e6eb0b0997414fbceb723ab3681e8d42","tid":1687036,"uid":156473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"a289cc847082bcaf237a9479cb3c7f945ed44fe6","tid":1687036,"uid":155339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"佢地已經變左選舉主任s"},{"pid":"109b0c993e9ce16cd42b02ef8dff2467c4c901fe","tid":1687036,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f1a4f6d7dded84579acb64cf03bfcab1a9b4ae","tid":1687036,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"甴近平"}]}